column17: A gas station in Bucharest, Bucharest, Romania.
column18: 4/3/2008: On Thursday, during the morning, an incendiary glass attack was signaled at a local gas station near a hotel where NATO officials were staying in Bucharest, Bucharest, Romania. One person was injured in the attack. No group claimed responsibility for the attack.
column64: The specific motive for the attack is unknown or was not reported.
column97: An incendiary glass attack wad done at the gas station.
